1931;;Sally in Our Alley;;British;;Maurice Elvey;;Gracie Fields, Ian Hunter;;comedy drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sally_in_Our_Alley_(1931_film);;A British soldier (Ian Hunter) goes off to fight in World War I, with his girlfriend (Gracie Fields) waiting and worried at home. He is soon wounded in battle and crippled. He comes to the conclusion that she would be better off believing that he has been killed so she can get on with her life. She gets the news and is devastated. Several years later she is still grieving for him, but he has now been cured and goes looking for her.